    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptionally well-kept mint-condition car that presents beautifully throughout and is the kind of example that stands out immediately. The paint, trim, interior, and overall finish show extremely light wear at most, and the car appears complete, highly maintained, and ready to enjoy right away. A buyer should expect a very clean, top-quality driver/showable example with excellent overall presentation.",
