      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition car that presents well inside and out and should make a very enjoyable driver. It appears to have been kept up better than an average older example, with a tidy interior, decent cosmetics, and no major signs of being a rough project or heavily worn-out car. Expect some normal age-related imperfections and minor blemishes, but overall this is a solid, well-sorted example that is ready to be used and enjoyed rather than needing immediate restoration.",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle is a straightforward budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project car, or a parts donor. It shows clear wear consistent with age and use, but it offers an affordable entry point with solid value for the right buyer. If you want a low-cost vehicle and understand what a bargain-priced used car represents, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s far from perfect, but it still has plenty to offer for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune. It shows its age and has its quirks, yet it\u2019s a great option for a handy buyer, a commuter on a budget, or anyone looking for a practical project. If you want something straightforward, approachable, and priced to make sense, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with a tough-running powertrain and plenty of usable life for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a straightforward project. Engine starts up, pulls through the rev range, and the transmission does its job well. Chassis feels sturdy, steering is predictable, and it has the kind of simple mechanical character that makes these easy to live with and maintain. It shows cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. Great opportunity to get into an affordable vehicle with good bones and practical upside.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Honest poor-condition driver with plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of presence you notice before you even turn the key\u2014a scrappy, honest machine with real personality and plenty of story left to write. It\u2019s the sort of ride that appeals to someone who sees possibility where others see a blank canvas: a weekend tinkerer, a practical buyer needing affordable wheels, or anyone drawn to a vehicle with charm, grit, and room to make it their own. If you\u2019ve been hunting for something inexpensive with unmistakable character, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers budget-friendly transportation with solid everyday usefulness and plenty of value for a buyer who wants an inexpensive car without pretense. A sensible choice for commuting, a first-time driver, or a light project, it presents as a straightforward opportunity at an accessible price.",
      "price": 5995.0,
